Please remember to sign your messages on talk pages by typing four tildes (<nowiki>~~~~</nowiki>); this will automatically insert your username and the date. If you need help, check out the [https://wiki.p2pfoundation.net/Main_Page official website], ask me on {{safesubst:<noinclude />#if:{{{1|}}}|[[user talk:{{{1}}}|my talk page]]|my talk page}}, or ask for help on your talk page, and a volunteer should respond shortly. Again, welcome!
